snippet.title: Piecing It Together Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist on Steam!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2665630/Piecing_It_Together

Piecing It Together brings jigsaw puzzles to a whole new dimension! 
Assemble 3D puzzles of beautiful dioramas, each brought to life by various artists.
Enjoy a quick puzzling session with just a handful of pieces, or challenge yourself with many!
